name: Rika Furude Theme - Roblox
description:
Check out the original style at userstyles.org
This is a follow-up to a request, I fulfil most, so go ahead and describe the pic you want in the comments or send an imgur link to it. If you find a better-quality image put an imgur link to it in the comments. All credits go to the mobile game>Higurashi no Naku Koro ni Mei< based on a murder mystery visual novel series of the same name. This code was created by me, do give feedback for improvements in the comments. If you want more fixed roblox styles just click BoopBop at the top, or you can click DittoDino below for some mediocre youtube progressbars.
